  "title": "DK Spawn",
  "description": "DK Spawn is a simple and efficient plugin to set the spawn point on your Minecraft server",
  "body": "🎯 What is DKSpawn?\nDKSpawn is a complete plugin for Minecraft Spigot/Paper 1.21 servers that provides an intuitive and robust system to manage player spawns.\n\n🚀 Main Features:\n\n**Admin System:**\n\n\n```/dksetspawn``` – Set a custom spawn point\n\n\n```/dkdespawn``` – Remove the defined spawn point\n\n**Teleport System (2 commands):**\n\n```/dkspawn``` – Teleport to spawn\n\n```/spawn``` – Teleport to spawn",
